Via Virt-Manager:

ADD HARDWARE CHANNEL
Name: org.qemu.guest_agent.0
Device type: UNIX socket (unix)
AUTO

Via CLI:

virsh shutdown VMNAME
virsh edit VMNAME

Adicione dentro de <devices>:

<channel type='unix'>
  <source mode='bind'/>
  <target type='virtio' name='org.qemu.guest_agent.0'/>
</channel>

virsh start VMNAME
